{"tid":861381,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"釗峰畀面幫Lokman拉票","createTime":"2018-10-14T05:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T05:48:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc4ff0907047a314673c77a916fd9f36304ab37","tid":861381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181014/20521758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F20521758&d=gVFI0nuS7Zb4WW4BWPLu8%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=731c5c88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F20521758&h=ca767b80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181014/20521758</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月14日 <br />\n<br />\n釗峰畀面幫Lokman拉票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181014/large/14ec1p31new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181014%2Flarge%2F14ec1p31new.jpg&h=22b4f241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n釗峰（右）昨表示替狄以達為Lokman（左）拉票，又大讚對方表演豐富。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV昨日在九龍灣為《造星》決賽舉行拜神儀式，獲梁釗峰及劉偉強導演等現身撐場，釗峰指要替好友狄以達為楊樂文（Lokman）拉票：「本身睇過佢做舞台劇，佢表演力好豐富。」Lokman更透露狄以達自薦做伴舞：「佢話如果有需要可以蒙面出場，但我冇應承，我搵咗其他兄弟。」他坦言有歌手支持有優勢，令觀眾更留意自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181014/large/14ec1p32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181014%2Flarge%2F14ec1p32.jpg&h=210c0255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚的評判劉偉強（右），昨亦有現身參與拜神儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於姜濤反而沒有呼籲粉絲投票，他說：「我性格就係咁，冇刻意叫，如果真心支持我，會自己來。」他笑言一切隨緣，入選已很開心，更打算完騷後與全部參賽者食飯慶功。陳卓賢（Ian）對於比賽未完已獲電視台賞識邀拍劇，他說：「參賽唔係以勝負為主，只係想多啲人認識、認同，𠵱家已達到。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：王連連<br />\n攝影︰林賓尼  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n賽前逐一點評　監製花姐彈懶音反白眼<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n光希、靜香後日襲港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賽前逐一點評監製花姐彈懶音反白眼<br />\n<br />\n《造星》今決賽六子自評勝算大熱姜濤　認清敵友"}]}